Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:06.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将这把剑从岩石中拔出的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就应当是不列颠之王
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.26,0:00:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔托莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.36,0:00:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在握住那东西前 还是再仔细想一想为好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.36,0:00:26.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦将其拔出 你就不再是人类了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber宁愿舍弃自身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.68,0:00:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要选择保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点 决不要忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 你肯成为我的Servant吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.06,0:00:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话就用不着杀你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.82,0:00:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿因兹贝伦城
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这里没错了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.29,0:01:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 不是开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.07,0:01:05.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别告诉我你忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.11,0:01:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手的那位忠诚部下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是面对什么样的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.30,0:01:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于Servant来说Master是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.54,0:01:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer隐去身形 Saber也快隐藏气息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊利雅斯菲尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.42,0:02:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,错觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.15,0:02:20.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差少许
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不快点去通知Saber她们的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.18,0:04:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在这种时候遇到巡逻的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:24.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.56,0:04:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我想问你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比预想中的要有精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来并不需要我们特意赶过来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是早说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.73,0:04:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去理会卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连远坂和Archer也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.02,0:04:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我拜托他们来营救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为士郎似乎被伊利雅斯菲尔给拐走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我们是合作关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 在伊利雅斯菲尔回来之前快走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:14.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.09,0:05:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber 果然身体还…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 十分惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 还是能成为士郎的盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在胡说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 肩膀借你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有必要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.95,0:05:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:39.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要幻想着你能拯救Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底你这家伙还不是什么也办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡的出口
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来还来得及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.37,0:06:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然说是出口 但这里是正门入口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说是最惹眼的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说太正大光明了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为对方不在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用最短的距离一口气冲出去是最佳选择吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:45.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊 这么快就要回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.32,0:06:48.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易才来一次的 真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊利雅斯菲尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.52,0:06:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.87,0:07:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能主动过来真太让我高兴了 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 默不作声很无聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得我给你们留下了点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:14.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想你们还是留下一份遗嘱比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那么我问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.78,0:07:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊利雅斯菲尔 感觉不到你回来的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:27.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 你一直隐藏在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦 我哪里也没有去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在这里欣赏着你们的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以离开城堡的是假货呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:41.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 因为我是这座城堡的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能不好好招待一下…客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有什么要说的了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.91,0:08:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发誓 今天不放过任何一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.88,0:08:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎 请快逃 这里由我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.36,0:08:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么 这种事我怎么做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer 听得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.20,0:08:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕就一会儿也好 你先一个人拖住那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太胡来了 你认真的吗 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer一个人根本敌不过Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.31,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们乘机逃跑 知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贤明的判断
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凛如果能先逃掉的话 我也能跑的掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.85,0:08:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且单独行动本来就是弓兵最擅长的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:08:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让我吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要用那名不见经传的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来阻止我的赫拉克勒斯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想不到你还有着这么可爱的地方呢 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.83,0:09:11.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以确认一件事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要争取时间是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过把那东西打倒也没什么关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:35.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我就应你所求吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:39.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 这种嚣张的家伙 把他给大卸八块了也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.18,0:09:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走 士郎 Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎 除此之外别无他法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:09:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫宫士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.78,0:10:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了 你不是战斗者 而只是生产者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去想多余的事 你能做到的事只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去试着把这件事做到极至
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别忘了 你应当想象的是最强的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去想什么外敌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.18,0:10:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的战斗对象 只是自己的想象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走哪边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:17.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全躲开了却还落得如此惨状
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.22,0:11:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快毁了他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好弱 还没得到表现的余地就坏掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然用这种宝具挑战Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.22,0:12:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.05,0:13:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还算是名不虚传呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.06,0:13:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:19.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,325)}{\fs20}身为剑体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:19.72,Niaoyu,NTP,0,0,0,,「 I am the bone of my sword 」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是Archer…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.67,0:13:56.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.18,0:14:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无论如何也一定要逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker居然会摆出防守的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 是投影了宝具…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.13,0:14:27.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是普通的Servant则立死无疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.51,0:14:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker 快去追
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管体型庞大却还真能动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,325)}{\fs20}钢铁之血        灼璃之心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.35,0:15:16.83,Niaoyu,NTP,0,0,0,,「 Steel is my body, and fire is my blood 」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,325)}{\fs20}手创千剑        历经百战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:28.60,Niaoyu,NTP,0,0,0,,「 I have created over a thousand blades 」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.11,0:15:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,325)}{\fs20}无一败绩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.11,0:15:42.70,Niaoyu,NTP,0,0,0,,「 Unknown to death 」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,325)}{\fs20}无一知己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.75,Niaoyu,NTP,0,0,0,,「 Nor known to Life 」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.13,0:15:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心技-泰山至 心技-黄河渡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手被毁了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.18,0:16:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确称得上是最强的Servant
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.84,0:17:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Archer他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完呢 那家伙还在努力着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:28.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下子 你总该有所后悔了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.71,0:17:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原以为自己已经斩断私情了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着 难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker 游戏结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.44,0:17:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要松懈不要犹豫 在自己被杀死之前解决掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:17:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是依旧毫不客气呢 伊莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.01,0:17:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.60,0:18:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我的败北已经无法改变
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但要了结我 可要耗费不少工夫呢 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.04,0:18:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不使出全力最好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.77,0:18:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此期间 我会再带走「两个」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有气息了 难道说逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来月之女神并没有庇佑你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:19:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,325)}{\fs20}常独自一人    自醉于剑丘之巅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:19:00.60,Niaoyu,NTP,0,0,0,,「 Have withstood pain to create many weapons 」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:10.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,325)}{\fs20}因此    此生亦无任何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.81,0:19:10.57,Niaoyu,NTP,0,0,0,,「 Yet, those hands will never hold anything 」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,325)}{\fs20}则其身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,325)}{\fs20}定为无限剑制
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:17.22,Niaoyu,NTP,0,0,0,,「 So as I pray 」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.00,0:19:21.82,Niaoyu,NTP,0,0,0,,「  unlimited blade works 」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs18}固有结界：极接近魔法的魔术。空想具现化的亚种，\N将心象世界化为实体侵蚀现实世界，创造出自己的世界。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:46.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,固有…结界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.20,0:20:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如你所见 你将要迎战的是无限之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.17,0:20:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑中之极至
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.92,0:20:18.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要畏畏缩缩的 尽管来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.50,0:20:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,远坂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.76,0:20:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊利雅斯菲尔很快就会追上来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:04.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是落得被他们杀死的下场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.17,0:21:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.01,0:21:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber Saber！！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.56,0:21:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker居然会5次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.41,0:21:41.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,5次被区区一个Servant所杀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.67,0:21:43.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事根本就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.99,0:21:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要和我说你是让着他的 Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.30,0:21:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶快将伤口愈合 我们这就去杀掉他们
